{"title":"Statistics at BEIS","public_updated_at":"2016-08-26T09:45:21Z","details":{"body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><h2 id=\"latest-statistics\">Latest statistics</h2>\n\n<p>View our <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/statistics?keywords=&amp;topics%5B%5D=all&amp;departments%5B%5D=department-for-business-energy-and-industrial-strategy&amp;from_date=&amp;to_date=\">latest statistics</a>. We also <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/statistics/announcements?utf8=%E2%9C%93&amp;organisations%5B%5D=department-for-business-energy-and-industrial-strategy\">announce publication dates for all national and official statistics</a> in advance.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"collections\">Collections</h2>\n\n<h3 id=\"emissions-and-climate-change-statistics\">Emissions and climate change statistics</h3>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/uk-greenhouse-gas-emissions-statistics\">UK greenhouse gas emissions</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Contact <a href=\"mailto:climatechange.statistics@beis.gov.uk\">climatechange.statistics@beis.gov.uk</a> if you have any enquiries.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"energy-sector-statistics\">Energy sector statistics</h3>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/total-energy-statistics\">total energy</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/coal-statistics\">coal</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/oil-statistics\">oil</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/gas-statistics\">gas</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/electricity-statistics\">electricity</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/renewables-statistics\">renewables</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/feed-in-tariff-statistics\">feed-in tariff</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/combined-heat-and-power-statistics\">combined heat and power</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/weather-statistics\">weather</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/foreign-energy-trade-statistics\">energy trade</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/calorific-values\">calorific values</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/energy-statistics-explanatory-notes\">energy sector statistics: explanatory notes</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Contact <a href=\"mailto:energy.stats@beis.gov.uk\">energy.stats@beis.gov.uk</a> if you have any enquiries.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"energy-price-statistics\">Energy price statistics</h3>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/domestic-energy-prices\">domestic energy price</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/industrial-energy-prices\">industrial energy price</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/road-fuel-and-other-petroleum-product-prices\">road fuel and other petroleum product price</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/international-energy-price-comparisons\">international energy price comparison</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Contact <a href=\"mailto:energy.stats@beis.gov.uk\">energy.stats@beis.gov.uk</a> if you have any enquiries.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"energy-efficiency-statistics\">Energy efficiency statistics</h3>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/household-energy-efficiency-national-statistics\">household energy efficiency</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/national-energy-efficiency-data-need-framework\">national energy efficiency data (NEED) framework</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/renewable-heat-incentive-statistics\">renewable heat incentive</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/smart-meters-statistics\">smart meters</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Contact <a href=\"mailto:energyefficiency.stats@beis.gov.uk\">energyefficiency.stats@beis.gov.uk</a> if you have any enquiries.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"sub-national-statistics\">Sub-national statistics</h3>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/regional-energy-data-guidance-note\">sub-national consumption statistics: methodology and guidance booklet</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/sub-national-electricity-consumption-data\">electricity consumption data</a></li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/sub-national-gas-consumption-data\">gas consumption data</a></p>\n  </li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/road-transport-consumption-at-regional-and-local-level\">road transport consumption data</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/sub-national-consumption-of-other-fuels\">consumption of other fuels</a></li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/total-final-energy-consumption-at-sub-national-level\">total fuel consumption data</a></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/northern-ireland-electricity-consumption-data\">Northern Ireland electricity consumption data</a></p>\n  </li>\n  <li><a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://tools.decc.gov.uk/en/content/cms/statistics/local_auth/interactive/domestic_ge/index.html\">electricity and gas interactive map</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/sub-national-electricity-and-gas-consumption-statistics-analysis-tool-2005-to-2009\">electricity and gas analysis tool</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Contact <a href=\"mailto:energyefficiency.stats@beis.gov.uk\">energyefficiency.stats@beis.gov.uk</a> if you have any enquiries.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"fuel-poverty-statistics\">Fuel poverty statistics</h3>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/fuel-poverty-statistics\">fuel poverty statistics</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/fuel-poverty-sub-regional-statistics\">fuel poverty sub-regional statistics</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Contact <a href=\"mailto:fuelpoverty@beis.gov.uk\">fuelpoverty@beis.gov.uk</a> if you have any enquiries.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"energy-statistics-publications-and-press-notices\">Energy statistics publications and press notices</h3>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/digest-of-uk-energy-statistics-dukes\">digest of UK energy statistics (DUKES)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/uk-energy-in-brief\">UK energy in brief</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/energy-flow-charts\">energy flow chart</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/energy-consumption-in-the-uk\">energy consumption in the UK</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/energy-trends\">energy trends</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/energy-trends-articles\">energy trends articles</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/quarterly-energy-prices\">quarterly energy prices</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/uk-energy-sector-indicators\">UK energy sector indicators</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Contact <a href=\"mailto:energy.stats@beis.gov.uk\">energy.stats@beis.gov.uk</a> if you have any enquiries.</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"statistics-for-local-authorities\">Statistics for local authorities</h3>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/interactive-maps-trends-in-fuel-poverty-energy-use-and-energy-efficiency-measures\">interactive maps: trends in fuel poverty, energy use and energy efficiency measures</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 id=\"other-beis-statistics\">Other <abbr title=\"Department for Business, Energy and Industrial Strategy\">BEIS</abbr> statistics</h3>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/business-population-estimates\">business population estimates</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/building-materials-and-components-monthly-statistics-2012\">building materials</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/community-innovation-survey\">community innovation survey</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/insolvency-service-official-statistics\">insolvency</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/trade-union-statistics\">trade unions</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/public-attitudes-tracking-survey\">energy and climate change public attitudes tracker</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/fuel-mix-disclosure-data-tables\">fuel mix disclosure data tables</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/radioactive-incident-monitoring\">radioactive incident monitoring</a></li>\n  <li><a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://ukinventory.nda.gov.uk/\">UK radioactive waste and materials inventory</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Higher and further education statistics, previously published by Department for Business, Innovation and Skills (<abbr title=\"Department for Business, Innovation and Skills\">BIS</abbr>), are now published by the <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/department-for-education/about/statistics\">Department for Education</a>.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"archived-statistics\">Archived statistics</h2>\n\n<p>GOV.UK offers the most recent statistics <abbr title=\"Department for Business, Energy and Industrial Strategy\">BEIS</abbr> has published. This includes statistics previously published by the <abbr title=\"Department for Business, Innovation and Skills\">BIS</abbr> and the Department of Energy and Climate Change (<abbr title=\"Department of Energy and Climate Change\">DECC</abbr>) (both now closed).</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"corporate-procedures-and-standards\">Corporate procedures and standards</h2>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"Department for Business, Energy and Industrial Strategy\">BEIS</abbr>, formerly <abbr title=\"Department for Business, Innovation and Skills\">BIS</abbr> and <abbr title=\"Department of Energy and Climate Change\">DECC</abbr>, has stated it has followed official guidelines on how it determines and presents statistics:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/statistics/code-of-practice-for-statistics-statement-of-compliance\">code of practice for statistics: <abbr title=\"Department for Business, Innovation and Skills\">BIS</abbr> statement of compliance</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/decc-statistics-governance\">code of practice for statistics: <abbr title=\"Department of Energy and Climate Change\">DECC</abbr> statement of compliance</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n</div>","organisation":"2bde479a-97f2-42b5-986a-287a623c2a1c","tags":{"browse_pages":[],"policies":[],"topics":[]}},"routes":[{"path":"/government/organisations/department-for-business-energy-and-industrial-strategy/about/statistics","type":"exact"}],"redirects":[],"publishing_app":"whitehall","rendering_app":"whitehall-frontend","need_ids":[],"phase":"live","analytics_identifier":null,"document_type":"statistics","schema_name":"corporate_information_page","first_published_at":"2016-08-26T09:45:23Z","base_path":"/government/organisations/department-for-business-energy-and-industrial-strategy/about/statistics","description":"We publish statistics on energy, climate change, energy efficiency, fuel poverty, building materials, economic performance and employment, innovation and trade union membership.","content_id":"4d8365be-29ca-49f5-9b07-ec0c6e17b82e","locale":"en","expanded_links":{"organisations":[{"analytics_identifier":"D1198","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/department-for-business-energy-and-industrial-strategy","base_path":"/government/organisations/department-for-business-energy-and-industrial-st